Class DoneEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
      • DoneEvent

  • class DoneEvent
extends Event
    DoneEvent corresponds to the event where a server is finished serving. It will generate a potential BreakEvent based on the paramters breakChance. If server does not go on break, it will serve the next customer automatically. DoneEvent will also recored time taken for customer to be served.
